    net.minecraftforge.registries.IForgeRegistryEntry<net.minecraft.block.Block>, IDynamicModelElement, IConfigurable<BlockConfig>, IConfigurableBlock, IGuiContainerProvider

    public abstract class ConfigurableBlockGui
extends ConfigurableBlock
implements IGuiContainerProvider
    Block without a tile entity with a GUI that can hold ExtendedConfigs. The container and GUI must be set inside the constructor of the extension.
